%2C%20compared%20to%20647%20across%20the%20whole%20of%202022.%20Across%20the%20US%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20die%20annually%20from%20an%20overdose%20of%20synthetic%20opioids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EUS-China%20Fentanyl%20Agreement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Biden%20said%20Beijing%20had%20agreed%20to%20stem%20the%20export%20of%20items%20related%20to%20the%20drug's%20production.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20going%20to%20save%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters%2C%20and%20said%20he%20appreciated%20China's%20%26quot%3Bcommitment%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20agreement%2C%20China%20will%20go%20after%20companies%20that%20make%20precursors%20-%20items%20needed%20to%20produce%20the%20opioid%20-%20a%20senior%20American%20official%20said.%20However%2C%20in%20a%20caveat%20underlining%20the%20distrust%20between%20the%20two%20sides%2C%20he%20said%20the%20US%20will%20%26quot%3Btrust%20but%20verify%26quot%3B%20China's%20actions%20against%20the%20drug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbiden-calls-xi-jinping-dictator-after-meeting-to-strike-deals-on-fentanyl-ai-4578143%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%20Calls%20Xi%20Jinping%20%26quot%3BDictator%26quot%3B%20After%20Striking%20Fentanyl%20Deal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChinese%20companies%20are%20a%20source%20of%20the%20opioid%20and%20chemicals%20which%20can%20be%20combined%20to%20make%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20White%20House%20statement%20after%20the%20meeting%20highlighted%20joint%20efforts%20to%20%26quot%3Bcombat%20global%20illicit%20drug%20manufacturing%20and%20trafficking%20(including%20fentanyl)...%20and%20establishment%20of%20a%20working%20group%20for%20ongoing%20communication%20and%20law%20enforcement%20coordination%20on%20counter-narcotics%20issues%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20also%20said%20Mr%20Biden%20stressed%20the%20need%20to%20counter%20the%20evolving%20threat%20of%20illicit%20synthetic%20drugs%20like%20fentanyl%2C%20and%20to%20fight%20supply%20of%20precursor%20chemicals%20and%20pills%20to%20cartels%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat%20Is%20Fentanyl%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPharmaceutical%20fentanyl%20is%20100%20times%20more%20potent%20than%20morphine%20and%2050%20times%20more%20so%20than%20heroin%2C%20and%20was%20approved%20by%20the%20US'%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20as%20an%20analgesic%20(pain%20relief)%20in%201998.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20prescription%20form%2C%20it%20is%20known%20by%20names%20like%20Actiq%2C%20Duragesic%2C%20and%20Sublimaze.%20The%20version%20linked%20to%20overdose%20deaths%20is%20an%20illegally%20made%20version.%20On%20the%20street%20it%20is%20also%20called%20China%20Girl%20and%20China%20Town.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20illicit%20fentanyl%20is%20made%20in%20labs%20outside%20the%20United%20States%20and%20smuggled%20across%20the%20Mexico%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFentanyl%2C%20like%20other%20opioid%20analgesics%2C%20leads%20to%20euphoria%2C%20pain%20relief%2C%20sedation%2C%20confusion%2C%20drowsiness%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20vomiting%2C%20as%20well%20as%20urinary%20retention%2C%20pupillary%20constriction%2C%20and%20respiratory%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHow%20Is%20It%20Consumed%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20prescription%20settings%20it%20can%20be%20administered%20as%20an%20injection%2C%20a%20patch%20to%20put%20on%20the%20skin%20or%20via%20pills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFentanyl%20for%20illegal%20consumption%20is%20available%20both%20as%20a%20liquid%20and%20powder.%20In%20the%20latter%20form%2C%20it%20can%20be%20administered%20via%20nasal%20sprays%20or%20eye%20drops%2C%20or%20even%20dropped%20into%20small%20candles.%20It%20is%20also%20sold%20as%20pills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20has%20labelled%20fentanyl%20and%20fentanyl-laced%20drugs%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20dangerous%26quot%3B%2C%20warning%20many%20may%20even%20be%20unaware%20their%20drugs%20are%20laced%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ESigns%20Of%20Overdose%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20CDC%2C%20some%20of%20the%20signs%20of%20a%20fentanyl%20overdose%20are%20constricted%20pupils%2C%20weak%20or%20slow%20breathing%2C%20choking%20or%20gurgling%20sounds%2C%20a%20limp%20body%20and%20discoloured%20or%20cold%2C%20or%20clammy%2C%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700119320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fb0o84s4_fentanyl-pill_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffentanyl-us-china-talks-biden-xi-jinping-ndtv-explains-what-is-fentanyl-synthetic-opioid-discussed-by-biden-xi-4578606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22United%20States%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20said%20Wednesday%20China%20will%20take%20steps%20to%20tackle%20the%20flow%20of%20fentanyl%20-%20a%20synthetic%20opioid%20responsible%20for%20the%20death%20of%20over%2070%2C000%20people%20last%20year%20-%20into%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffentanyl-us-china-talks-biden-xi-jinping-ndtv-explains-what-is-fentanyl-synthetic-opioid-discussed-by-biden-xi-4578606%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffentanyl-us-china-talks-biden-xi-jinping-ndtv-explains-what-is-fentanyl-synthetic-opioid-discussed-by-biden-xi-4578606%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffentanyl-us-china-talks-biden-xi-jinping-ndtv-explains-what-is-fentanyl-synthetic-opioid-discussed-by-biden-xi-4578606%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UCO%20Bank%20recovers%2079%25%20of%20wrongly%20credited%20amount%20after%20technical%20glitch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700118925000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-08%2F09%2F