d%20their%20support.%20The%20UN%20resolution%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20was%20opposed%20by%20some%20Western%20powers%20and%20shamefully%2C%20India%20abstained.%20True%2C%20India%20sent%20token%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Palestine.%20Various%20columnists%20in%20India%20commented%20on%20the%20ghastly%20phenomenon.%20Most%20of%20them%20blamed%20the%20tragedy%20on%20Hamas%2C%20many%20called%20it%20a%20jihadi%20terrorist%20organisation%2C%20and%20characterised%20their%20unabashed%20support%20of%20Israel%20as%20%E2%80%98zero%20tolerance%E2%80%99%20of%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Egodi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20media%20is%20glorifying%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20condemning%20the%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%20Hamas.%20Many%20pro-Palestine%20demonstrations%20were%20held%20in%20India%2C%20but%20police%20in%20Delhi%2C%20UP%20and%20even%20Opposition-ruled%20Bengaluru%20and%20Kolkata%20have%20denied%20permission%20to%20protests%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20aggression.%20In%20UP%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20no%20opposition%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20official%20position%20would%20be%20permitted.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Western%20world%20saw%20a%20plethora%20of%20protests%20in%20which%2C%20interestingly%2C%20many%20Jews%20have%20been%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20social%20media%20is%20full%20of%20opposition%20to%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20and%20is%20presenting%20Israel%20as%20a%20victim%20of%20Hamas.%20Yet%2C%20since%20the%20day%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attack%20on%20October%207%2C%20social%20media%20has%20seen%20more%20and%20more%20Islamophobic%20posts%2C%20guided%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20IT%20cell.%20The%20Palestinian%20cause%20is%20presented%20as%20Islamist%2C%20and%20so%20we%20must%20support%20Israel.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20total%20conflation%20of%20the%20already%20prevailing%20domestic%20Islamophobia%20in%20India%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20scathing%20Islamophobic%20posts%2C%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%20have%20come%20from%20India.%20The%20peak%20of%20this%20phenomenon%2C%20equating%20Hamas%20with%20Palestine%20and%20presenting%20it%20as%20a%20terrorist%20jihadi%20organisation%2C%20was%20witnessed%20in%20IIT-Bombay.%20Here%2C%20a%20humanities%20faculty%20member%20outlined%20the%20history%20of%20Palestine%20and%20Israel%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20Hamas%20in%20a%20class.%20In%20the%20same%20department%2C%20Sudhanva%20Deshpande%2C%20noted%20cultural%20worker%20from%20the%20Jan%20Natya%20Manch%2C%20showed%20a%20documentary%20and%20outlined%20the%20resistance%20to%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20in%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20(on%20November%2012%2C%202023)%2C%20students%20affiliated%20to%20the%20RSS-backed%20Vivek%20Vichar%20Manch%20protested%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fiitb-faculty-members-speak-up-for-prof-say-student-aggressive%2Farticleshow%2F105247329.cms%5C%22%3Edemanded%20the%20suspension%20of%20the%20faculty%20member.%3C%2Fa%3E%20VVM%20students%20took%20out%20a%20procession%20along%20with%20people%20from%20outside%20the%20campus%20and%20gave%20the%20call%20for%20%E2%80%98goli%20maro%20(shoot%20them)%E2%80%99.%20They%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20the%20faculty%20member%20and%20Deshpande%20for%20eulogising%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20and%20demanded%20a%20probe%20by%20central%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20question%20of%20academic%20freedom%2C%20this%20raises%20many%20others.%20How%20is%20the%20Israeli%20occupation%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20resistance%20being%20seen%3F%20It%20is%20heartening%20that%20India%20has%20voted%20for%20the%20UN%20resolution%20against%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20make%20settlements%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20ongoing%20aggression%20in%20Gaza%20by%20Israel%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20context.%20As%20UN%20Secretary%20General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHamas%20has%20not%20come%20from%20a%20vacuum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoam%20Chomsky%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20old%20man%20in%20Gaza%20held%20a%20placard%20that%20read%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20take%20my%20water%2C%20burn%20my%20olive%20trees%2C%20destroy%20my%20house%2C%20take%20my%20job%2C%20steal%20my%20land%2C%20imprison%20my%20father%2C%20kill%20my%20mother%2C%20bombard%20my%20country%2C%20starve%20us%20all%2C%20humiliate%20us%20all%2C%20but%20I%20am%20to%20blame%3A%20I%20shot%20a%20rocket%20back.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blockade%20of%20Gaza%20has%20lasted%2016%20years%20and%20the%20occupation%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%20has%20lasted%2056%20years%3B%20the%20dispossession%20of%20Palestinians%20of%20their%20lands%20and%20homes%20began%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20Israel%2C%20an%20ethno-supremacist%20state%2C%20in%201948.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhindutva-israel-tweets-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3EUnpacking%20the%20Hindutva%20Embrace%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resistance%20in%20Palestine%20has%20gone%20through%20various%20phases.%20Black%20September%20killed%20Israeli%20athletes%20in%20the%20Munich%20Olympics%20in%201972%2C%20after%2014%20lakh%20Palestinians%20were%20made%20refugees.%20Yasser%20Arafat%20also%20was%20doomed%20to%20failure%20as%20the%20Western%20powers%20tried%20to%20impose%20humiliating%20conditions%20on%20the%20Palestinians.%20Hamas%20is%20not%20the%20leadership%20of%20choice%2C%20for%20sure%2C%20but%20what%20is%20the%20way%20for%20the%20democratic%20expression%20of%20resistance%20when%20Gaza%20has%20been%20treated%20as%20an%20open%20prison%20by%20Israel%3F%20Israel%20has%20violated%20most%20of%20the%20UN%20resolutions%20seeking%20peace%20and%20justice.%20It%20is%20the%20aggressive%20occupier%20now%20eying%20the%20offshore%20gas%20reserves%20in%20Gaza%2C%20valued%20at%20around%20%2464%20billion.%20Israel%20has%20struck%20deals%20with%20US%20and%20European%20companies%20to%20become%20an%20exporter%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%E2%80%98common%20sense%E2%80%99%20being%20promoted%20in%20India%20compares%20Hamas%20to%20the%20jihadi%20terrorism%20which%20culminated%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20Al%20Qaeda%2C%20Taliban%20and%20IS.%20This%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98Islamic%20terrorism%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20concoction%20in%20recent%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20US%20promoted%20fundamentalist%20groups%2C%20trained%20Muslim%20youth%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20madrasas%20and%20armed%20them%20is%20not%20a%20secret.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20Hillary%20Clinton%20had%20stated%20that%20they%20trained%20the%20Mujahideen%20to%20go%20after%20Russians%20in%20Afghanistan.%20In%20his%20book%20Good%20Muslim%2C%20Bad%20Muslim%20(Harmony%2C%202003)%2C%20based%20on%20CIA%20papers%2C%20Mahmood%20Mamdani%20tells%20us%20that%20America%20spent%20%248%2C000%20million%20and%20provided%207%2C000%20tons%20of%20armaments%20to%20train%20the%20Mujahideen%20and%20Al%20Qaeda.%20After%209%2F11%20US%20media%20coined%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98Islamic%20terrorism%E2%80%99%2C%20Islamophobia%20was%20the%20main%20thrust%20of%20the%20US%20propaganda%20machine%2C%20which%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20global%20media.%20In%20India%2C%20it%20became%20an%20add-on%20to%20the%20prevailing%20anti-Muslim%20%E2%80%98communal%20common%20sense%E2%80%99%20which%20came%20to%20rule%20the%20godi%20media%2C%20social%20media%20and%20corporate-controlled%20TV%20channels%2C%20aided%20by%20word-of-mouth%20propaganda%20by%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20has%20led%20to%20the%20current%20dismal%20situation%2C%20where%20in%20an%20academic%20institution%20an%20invited%20talk%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20Israel%2C%20its%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20its%20designs%20on%20gas%20reserves%20is%20seen%20as%20promoting%20terrorism!%20Israel%20is%20probably%20the%20only%20modern%20example%20of%20a%20nation%20formed%20by%20immigrants%20who%20gradually%20displaced%20the%20mass%20of%20humanity%20living%20in%20the%20region%2C%20who%20are%20not%20permitted%20any%20democratic%20expressions%20of%20resistance.%20And%20when%20Hamas%20offers%20a%20ferocious%20attack%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20excuse%20to%20pounce%20upon%20the%20whole%20nation%20of%20Palestine%20with%20barbaric%20force!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20Puniyani%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20of%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700116729000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16120732%2Fimage1170x530cropped-5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fisraeli-onslaught-on-palestine-is-a-boost-to-indian-islamophobia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20dismal%20situation%20when%20in%20an%20academic%20institution%20an%20invited%20talk%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20formation%20of%20Israel%2C%20its%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20and%20its%20designs%20on%20gas%20reserves%20is%20seen%20as%20promoting%20terrorism.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fisraeli-onslaught-on-palestine-is-a-boost-to-indian-islamophobia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan-Set%20Oscar%20Contender%20%E2%80%9