ah%2C%20Laila%20Elhaddad%2C%20Waeil%20Elbhassi%2C%20Basim%20Elkarra%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CA.N.%E2%80%9D%2C%20who%20are%20US%20citizens%20with%20family%20in%20Gaza%3B%20and%20Omar%20Al-Najjar%2C%20a%20medical%20intern%20at%20Nasser%20Medical%20Complex%20in%20Khan%20Yunis.%20All%20have%20had%20multiple%20family%20members%20killed%2C%20subjected%20to%20the%20closure%20of%20Gaza%2C%20and%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petitioners%2C%20Biden%2C%20Blinken%2C%20and%20Austin%20are%20%E2%80%9Csued%20in%20their%20official%20capacity%20for%20failing%20to%20prevent%20an%20unfolding%20genocide%20where%20they%20have%20influence%20over%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%20to%20do%20so%2C%20and%20directly%20abetting%20its%20development%20with%20weapons%2C%20funds%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20cover%2C%20in%20breach%20of%20duties%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20and%20customary%20international%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20is%20accompanied%20by%20a%20declaration%20from%20William%20Schabas%2C%20a%20leading%20legal%20expert%20on%20genocide%2C%20who%20identifies%20features%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20statements%2C%20deadly%20military%20assault%2C%20and%20total%20siege%20as%20signs%20of%20genocide.%20He%20affirms%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20breach%20of%20its%20legal%20duty%20to%20prevent%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20another%20expert%20declaration%20by%20the%20genocide%20and%20Holocaust%20scholars%20John%20Cox%2C%20Victoria%20Sanford%2C%20and%20Barry%20Trachtenberg%2C%20explains%20%E2%80%9Chow%20the%20genocidal%20intentions%20and%20actions%20of%20Israeli%20leadership%20resemble%20other%20genocides%20in%20recent%20history%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20last%20five%20weeks%2C%20President%20Biden%20and%20Secretaries%20Blinken%20and%20Austin%20have%20stood%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20an%20Israeli%20government%20that%20has%20made%20clear%20its%20intention%20to%20destroy%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20in%20Gaza.%20As%20neighbourhood%20after%20neighbourhood%2C%20hospital%20after%20hospital%2C%20and%20sheltering%20displaced%20Palestinians%20were%20bombed%2C%20while%20subject%20to%20a%20total%20siege%20and%20closure%20that%20denies%202.2%20million%20people%20basic%20necessities%20for%20life%2C%20they%20have%20continued%20to%20provide%20both%20military%20and%20political%20support%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unfolding%20genocidal%20campaign%20while%20imposing%20no%20red%20lines%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Katherine%20Gallagher%2C%20a%20senior%20attorney%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Constitutional%20Rights%20(CCR)%20and%20one%20of%20the%20lawyers%20who%20brought%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECCR%20has%20filed%20the%20case%20on%20behalf%20of%20petitioners%20in%20the%20court.%20According%20to%20the%20press%20statement%2C%20the%20United%20States%20has%20a%20duty%20under%20Article%201%20of%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20to%20prevent%20and%20punish%20acts%20of%20genocide%2C%20an%20obligation%20the%20US%20Congress%20made%20law%20in%201988%20when%20it%20ratified%20the%20Convention%20and%20passed%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%20Implementation%20Act%20(18%20U.S.C.%20%C2%A7%201091).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700112782000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19101948%2FF8uduyaWoAAr3mW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestinians-sue-biden-blinken-other-us-officials-for-supporting-israels-war-on-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20petitioners%20urged%20a%20federal%20court%20in%20the%20US%20to%20prevent%20the%20US%20administration%20from%20providing%20arms%2C%20money%2C%20and%20diplomatic%20support%20to%20Israel%20as%20there%20is%20an%20'unfolding%20genocide'%20by%20Israel%20against%20the%20civilian%20population%20of%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestinians-sue-biden-blinken-other-us