F%20general%20secretary%20Muan%20Tombing%20has%20said%20that%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20in%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Churachandpur%20districts%20will%20come%20under%20the%20ambit%20of%20self-rule%20and%20that%20the%20community%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20expectation%20from%20the%20Meitei%20Manipur%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20care%20if%20the%20Centre%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20recognise%20us.%20The%20plan%20has%20been%20under%20discussion%20for%20the%20past%20one%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20crucially%2C%20added%20that%20it%20was%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cselective%20justice%E2%80%9D%20that%20led%20the%20body%20to%20announce%20self-rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ago%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-tribal-group-gives-ultimatum-will-set-up-self-govt-9028350%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20ITLF%20had%20given%20an%20ultimatum%20that%20it%20will%20set%20up%20a%20self%20government%20if%20its%20demands%20are%20not%20met%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhether%20the%20central%20government%20recognises%20it%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20northeastern%20state%20has%20been%20severely%20divided%20along%20ethnic%20lines%20ever%20since%20violence%20erupted%20on%20May%203.%20Hundreds%20have%20died%2C%20more%20are%20injured%20and%20tens%20of%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced.%20The%20violence%20also%20led%20to%20Kuki-Zo%20MLAs%20and%20prominent%20citizens%20pressing%20for%20a%20separate%20territory%20for%20them.%20They%20had%20also%20said%20multiple%20times%20that%20the%20Meitei-majority%20government%20under%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20has%20lost%20their%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EITLF%E2%80%99s%20Muan%20Tombing%20said%20that%20the%20community%20will%20have%20a%20separate%20chief%20minister.%20Besides%2C%20those%20governmen