law%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Conricus%20said%20inside%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20and%20the%20camerapersons%20then%20proceed%20to%20the%20MRI%20room%20where%20they%20find%20military%20%26quot%3Bgrab-bags%26quot%3B%20-%20bags%20filled%20with%20weapons%20and%20ammunition%20for%20grab-and-go%20situations%20in%20a%20war%20zone.%20The%20camera%20zoomed%20in%20on%20the%20bag%20which%20clearly%20showed%20an%20AK-47%2C%20cartridges%20and%20a%20grenade%2C%20among%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20weapons%20have%20absolutely%20no%20business%20being%20inside%20a%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Conricus%20said%20in%20the%20IDF%20video.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20they%20are%20here%20is%20because%20Hamas%20put%20them%20here%20because%20they%20use%20this%20place%20like%20many%20other%20hospitals%20and%20ambulances%20for%20illicit%20military%20purposes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Israeli%20military%20and%20Hamas%20have%20accused%20each%20other%20of%20waging%20a%20%26quot%3Bpropaganda%20war%26quot%3B%20against%20each%20other%20since%20the%20region%20plunged%20into%20chaos%20following%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20Morphed%20images%2C%20decontextualised%20videos%20unrelated%20to%20the%20ongoing%20crisis%20have%20often%20been%20found%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20with%20illegitimate%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20authentic%20footage%20and%20firsthand%20accounts%20of%20the%20destruction%20have%20been%20circulated%20extensively%2C%20there%20have%20also%20been%20occurrences%20of%20people%20disseminating%20misinformation%20and%20misrepresenting%20videos%20from%20unrelated%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20IDF%20claimed%20yesterday%20that%20a%20Hamas-operated%20tunnel%20that%20leads%20to%20Gaza's%20Rantsi%20hospital.%20In%20a%20video%20quite%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20released%20today%2C%20IDF%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20enters%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20Ransi%20hospital%2C%20through%20the%20tunnel%2C%20where%20he%20finds%20%26quot%3Boperational%20gears%26quot%3B%20of%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hagari%20then%20points%20to%20a%20poster%20carrying%20Arabic%20inscriptions%20on%20a%20wall%2C%20claiming%20it%20to%20mention%20%26quot%3BOperation%20Al-Aqsa%20Flood%26quot%3B%20-%20the%20name%20given%20to%20the%20October%207%20Hamas%20attack%20-%20and%20a%20roster%20of%20Hamas%20operatives%20guarding%20Israeli%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20multiple%20fact-checkers%20have%20refuted%20the%20claim%20and%20countered%20that%20the%20inscriptions%20are%20just%20days%20of%20the%20week%20written%20in%20Arabic%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700108880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2mbq5t2o_idf-video-screengrab-shifa-hospital_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-al-shifa-hospital-hamas-israel-shares-video-of-hamas-weapons-stocked-in-gaza-hospitals-mri-unit-4578166%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20has%20claimed%20that%20its%20forces%20have%20found%20evidence%20that%20Hamas%20uses%20hospitals%20to%20store%20explosives%20and%20weapons%20for%20terror%20activities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-al-shifa-hospital-hamas-israel-shares-video-of-hamas-weapons-stocked-in-gaza-hospitals-mri-unit-4578166%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-al-shifa-hospital-hamas-israel-shares-video-of-hamas-weapons-stocked-in-gaza-hospitals-mri-unit-4578166%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-gaza-al-shifa-hospital-hamas-israel-shares-video-of-hamas-weapons-stocked-in-gaza-hospitals-mri-unit-4578166%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jaguar%20asked%20to%20pay%20Chennai%20bizman%20Rs%2042%20lakh%22%2C%22conte