2F11%2F16092457%2F05b-2018-APRIL-18-5-PS-Sankariah-Nine_deca.max-1400x1120-1-300x229.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16092457%2F05b-2018-APRIL-18-5-PS-Sankariah-Nine_deca.max-1400x1120-1-1024x781.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684997%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22915%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESankariah%20and%20V.S.%20Achuthanandan%2C%20the%20last%20living%20members%20of%20the%2032%20who%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20CPI%20National%20Council%20meeting%20in%201964%2C%20being%20felicitated%20at%20that%20party%E2%80%99s%2022nd%20congress%20in%202018%20by%20party%20General%20Secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury.%20Photo%3A%20S.%20Gavaskar%2F%20People%E2%80%99s%20Archive%20of%20Rural%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20Ramamurti%20filed%20his%20nomination%20while%20in%20detention%2C%20before%20the%20superintendent%20of%20the%20central%20jail.%20He%20contested%20the%201952%20election%20to%20the%20Madras%20Assembly%20from%20Madurai%20North%20constituency.%20I%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20his%20campaign.%20The%20other%20two%20candidates%20were%20Chidambaram%20Bharati%2C%20a%20veteran%20congressman%2C%20and%20P.T.%20Rajan%20from%20the%20Justice%20Party.%20Ramamurti%20won%20handsomely%2C%20the%20result%20was%20announced%20while%20he%20was%20still%20in%20jail.%20Bharati%20came%20second%20and%20Rajan%20lost%20his%20deposit.%20The%20victory%20meeting%20drew%20over%203%20lakh%20people%20to%20celebrate%20the%20win.%E2%80%9D%20Ramamurti%20emerged%20the%20first%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20after%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20communist%20party%20split%20in%201964%2C%20Sankariah%20went%20with%20the%20newly%20formed%20CPI-M.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%2032%20members%20who%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20CPI%20National%20Council%20in%201964%2C%20myself%20and%20V.%20S.%20Achuthanandan%20are%20the%20only%20two%20members%20still%20alive%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Sankariah%20went%20on%20to%20become%20general%20secretary%20and%20later%20president%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Sabha%2C%20still%20the%20largest%20farmers%20organisation%20in%20India%20with%2015%20million%20members.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20CPI-M%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20secretary%20for%20seven%20years%20and%20on%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20central%20committee%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20the%20first%20to%20introduce%20Tamil%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20assembly.%20In%201952%2C%20there%20was%20no%20provision%20to%20speak%20in%20Tamil%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20English%20was%20the%20only%20language%2C%20but%20%5Bour%20MLAs%5D%20Jeevanandam%20and%20Ramamurthy%20spoke%20in%20Tamil%20though%20the%20provision%20for%20it%20came%20only%206%20or%207%20years%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESankariah%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20the%20working%20class%20and%20peasantry%20remains%20undiminished.%20He%20believes%20the%20communists%20will%20%E2%80%9Cfind%20the%20correct%20answers%20to%20electoral%20politics%E2%80%9D%20and%20build%20mass%20movements%20on%20a%20greater%20scale.%20An%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20into%20the%20interview%2C%20the%2099-year-old%20is%20still%20talking%20with%20the%20same%20passion%20and%20energy%20with%20which%20he%20began.%20His%20spirit%20remains%20that%20of%20the%209-year-old%20who%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20inspired%20by%20the%20sacrifice%20of%20Bhagat%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20My%20thanks%20to%20Kavitha%20Muralidharan%20for%20her%20invaluable%20inputs%20in%20the%20making%20of%20this%20story.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2Fen%2Farticles%2Fsankariah-nine-decades-a-revolutionary%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fruralindiaonline.org%2F%5C%22%3EPeople%E2%80%99s%20Archive%20of%20R