%3Fall%3Dfalse%26sourceType%3Dap%26dateRangeType%3Dlive%26mediaSortType%3Dnewest%26pagesize%3D100%26viewType%3Dconversation%26keyword%3Dwire%3Adsa%2520AND%2520Biden%26storyType%3Dpublished%26mediatype%3Dtext%26pagenumber%3D0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeeting%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperative%20conference%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20said%20he%20discussed%20with%20Israelis%20their%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Bbe%20incredibly%20careful%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20worked%20to%20clear%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20fleeing%20Israeli%20bombardment%20were%20sheltering%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20most%20left%20in%20recent%20days%20as%20the%20fighting%20drew%20closer.%20The%20fate%20of%20premature%20babies%20at%20the%20hospital%20has%20drawn%20particular%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Health%20Ministry%20said%2040%20patients%2C%20including%20three%20babies%2C%20have%20died%20since%20Shifa's%20emergency%20generator%20ran%20out%20of%20fuel%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20word%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20another%2036%20babies%20the%20ministry%20said%20earlier%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20dying%20because%20there%20is%20no%20power%20for%20incubators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20Israel's%20raid%2C%20the%20United%20States%20said%20its%20own%20intelligence%20indicated%20militants%20have%20used%20Shifa%20and%20other%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20tunnels%20beneath%20them%20%E2%80%94%20to%20support%20military%20operations%20and%20hold%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%20hospitals%20can%20lose%20their%20protected%20status%20if%20combatants%20use%20them%20for%20military%20purposes.%20But%20civilians%20must%20be%20given%20ample%20time%20to%20flee%2C%20and%20any%20attack%20must%20be%20proportional%20to%20the%20military%20objective