588dc55d149cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnikki-haley-will-back-trump-if-he-clinches-gop-nomination-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nikki%20Haley%20doesn't%20think%20Trump%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20president%20going%20forward%26quot%3B%20but%20is%20willing%20to%20back%20his%20nomination%20anyway.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40insider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnikki-haley-will-back-trump-if-he-clinches-gop-nomination-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Biden%20and%20Xi%20Meet%2C%20What%E2%80%99s%20at%20Stake%20is%20Two%20Competing%20Visions%20for%20the%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16090026%2FUntitled-design-6-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeaving%20the%20Kremlin%20after%20his%20March%202023%20visit%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20said%20to%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20full%20view%20of%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%98Right%20now%20there%20are%20changes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20for%20100%20years%20%E2%80%93%20and%20we%20are%20the%20ones%20driving%20these%20changes%20together.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EXi%20was%20neither%20being%20pompous%20nor%20was%20he%20exaggerating.%20Together%20with%20Putin%2C%20Xi%20has%20unveiled%20an%20unparalleled%20and%20unbeatable%20vision%20of%20the%20new%20world%20order.%20Premised%20on%20the%20Chinese%20philosophy%20of%20win-win%20as%20against%20the%20traditional%20geopolitical%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emantra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20zero-sum%2C%20Xi%20is%20looking%20at%20uniting%20the%20world%20through%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI)%2C%20a%20network%20of%20cooperative%20roads%2C%20seas%20lanes%2C%20and%20hard%20and%20soft%20cyberspace%20connectivity%20for%20seamless%20flow%20of%20trade%20and%20traffic.%20This%20vision%20is%20complimented%20by%20Putin%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98pivot%20to%20Asia%E2%80%99%20vision%20spelt%20out%20in%202012%20for%20Greater%20Eurasia%20(Eurasia%20plus%20ASEAN%2C%20India%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20Arab%20world%2C%20and%20Iran)%20which%20seeks%20to%20create%20an%20economic%20cooperation%20zone%20from%20Eurasia%20(Russia%2C%20Belarus%2C%20Armenia%2C%20Kazakhstan%2C%20Kyrgyzstan)%20to%20the%20Asia-Pacific%2C%20thereby%20fusing%20the%20two%20visions%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20Global%20South%20(barring%20India)%20sees%20in%20these%20%E2%80%98once%20in%20a%20100-year%20changes%E2%80%99%20an%20opportunity%20to%20uplift%20its%20people%20and%20economy%20was%20evident%20from%20the%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Forum%20(BRF)%20to%20mark%20the%2010%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20BRI%20held%20in%20Beijing%20on%20October%2017%20and%2018.%20Nearly%20150%20Global%20South%20nations%20had%20representation%20at%20the%20Forum%20with%2023%20heads%20of%20the%20state%20participating%20in%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20Putin%20was%20the%20guest%20of%20honour.%20And%20India%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-and-china-are-trapped-in-a-conflict-of-their-own-making%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20China%20are%20Trapped%20in%20a%20Conflict%20of%20Their%20Own%20Making%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20two%20global%20powers%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20are%20forging%20a%20path%20towards%20a%20new%20cooperative%20world%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20third%20global%20power%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20still%20tied%20to%20old%20ideas%20of%20competition%2C%20is%20floundering%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20vision%20for%20the%20new%20world.%20This%20confusion%20was%20summed%20up%20by%20US%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20Jake%20Sullivan%20recently.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20essay%20in%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EForeign%20Affairs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Fauthors%2Fjake-sullivan%5C%22%3E%20magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20(November%2FDecember%202023)%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20America%20must%20adjust%20to%20%E2%80%98the%20main%20challenge%20it%20faces%3A%20competition%20(with%20China)%20in%20an%20age%20of%20interdependence.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20world%20is%20interdependent%2C%20the%20natural%20thing%20should%20be%20cooperation%20and%20not%20competition.%20And%20since%20there%20is%20a%20thin%20line%20between%20competition%20and%20conflict%2C%20in%20his%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20address%20in%20February%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20clarified%20that%20%E2%80%98the%20US%20seeks%20competition%2C%20not%20conflict.%E2%80%99%20Worse%2C%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20on%20what%20the%20competition%20should%20deliver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20most%20agree%20that%20like%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20during%20the%20Cold%20War%2C%20disintegration%20of%20China%20cannot%20be%20the%20end-state%20%E2%80%93%20especially%20since%20it%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20manufacturing%20hub%20and%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20primary%20trading%20partner%20of%20nearly%20138%20nations.%20Despite%20tensions%2C%20the%20total%20value%20in%20goods%20trade%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20in%202022-2023%20stood%20at%20US%24%20690%20billion.%20So%2C%20the%20ideal%20end-state%20from%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20point%20of%20view%20is%20one%20where%20there%20is%20a%20distinctive%20tilt%20in%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2F%20partners.%20This%20requires%20a%20new%20Cold%20War%20where%20the%20US%20plays%20to%20its%20advantage%3A%20military%20power%20or%20deterrence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20adopted%20a%20four-pronged%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%2C%20while%20overplaying%20the%20Chinese%20theft%20of%20US%20cutting-edge%20technologies%20by%20cyber%20means%2C%20Washington%20has%20adopted%20a%20%E2%80%98small%20yard%20and%20high%20fence%E2%80%99%20strategy%20to%20deny%20advanced%20processors%20(7nm%20and%20below)%20to%20China.%20According%20to%20the%20US%2C%20China%20will%20use%20these%20advanced%20microchips%20for%20new%20breakthroughs%20in%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%2C%20quantum%20computing%20and%20biotechnology%20to%20threaten%20its%20and%20its%E2%80%99%20allies%E2%80%99%20national%20security.%20The%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20US%2C%20which%20led%20the%20world%20in%20the%20third%20industrial%20revolution%20by%20semiconductors%2C%20mainframe%20computers%2C%20personal%20computers%2C%20and%20the%20internet%2C%20worries%20that%20China%20could%20leapfrog%20in%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution%20with%20AI%20and%20data%20since%205G%20wireless%20connectivity%2C%20which%20is%20the%20backbone%20of%20this%20revolution%2C%20has%20already%20been%20rolled%20out%20by%20China%E2%80%99s%20Huawei.%20This%20could%20make%20China%20the%20leader%20in%20setting%20international%20standards%20for%20the%20whole%20range%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20across%20the%20physical%2C%20digital%20and%20biological%20domains.%20Moreover%2C%20to%20ensure%20on-shoring%20and%20friendly-shoring%20of%20an%20advanced%20AI%20hardware%20ecosystem%2C%20the%20US%20passed%20the%20Chips%20and%20Science%20Act%2C%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20and%20the%20Infrastructure%20Investment%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20to%20protect%20its%20advantages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%2C%20the%20US%20is%20strengthening%20its%20deterrence%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20by%20reinforcing%20existing%20alliances%2C%20and%20by%20forming%20new%20one%E2%80%99s%20like%20AUKUS%20(Australia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20US).%20Called%20Integrated%20Deterrence%2C%20this%20includes%20a%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20India%20(given%20its%20sensitive%20location%20in%20the%20Indo%20Pacific)%20bilaterally%20%E2%80%93%20via%20the%20US-India%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technologies%20(ICET)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20multilaterally%20through%20the%20QUAD%20(quadrilateral%20security%20grouping%20of%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Australia).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%2C%20to%20meet%20the%20military%20challenge%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20combine%2C%20the%20US%20has%20connected%20its%20alliances%20in%20Europe%20with%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20by%20globalising%20NATO.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%2C%20to%20showcase%20that%20its%20balancing%20against%20China%20has%20both%20military%20and%20economic%20initiatives%2C%20the%20US%20has%20announced%20numerous%20international%20infrastructure%20building%20agreements%20like%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20Economic%20Framework%2C%20Build%20Back%20Better%20World%2C%20and%20the%20recent%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20none%20come%20close%20to%20the%20BRI%20where%20China%2C%20through%20the%20Asian%20Infrastructure%20Investment%20Bank%2C%20Silk%20Road%20Fund%2C%20China%20Development%20Bank%2C%20and%20Exim%20Bank%20has%20already%20invested%20US%24%20one%20trillion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20above%20military%20steps%2C%20the%20US%20hopes%20to%20disallow%20free%20movement%20to%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA)%20within%20the%20First%20Island%20Chain%20in%20the%20west%20Pacific%20where%20China%20has%20two%20of%20its%20total%20three%20core%20concerns%3A%20Taiwan%20and%20South%20China%20Sea%20(SCS)%3B%20the%20third%20being%20India%E2%80%99s%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20which%20China%20calls%20south%20Tibet%20or%20Zangnan.%20With%20growing%20PLA%20capabilities%2C%20China%20has%20taken%20a%20strong%20stand%20against%20US%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20air%20patrols%20in%20the%20SCS%20and%20its%20arming%20of%20Taiwan.%20While%20most%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20west%20Pacific%20theatre%20is%20a%20likely%20flash%20point%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%2C%20it%20appears%20unlikely.%20Great%20powers%20do%20not%20go%20to%20war%20directly%20since%20neither%20will%20be%20able%20to%20exercise%20enough%20war%20control%20to%20achieve%20desired%20military%20objectives%2C%20nor%20have%20escalation%20control%20to%20limit%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20with%20US%20involvement%20in%20Ukraine%20(by%20proxy)%20and%20directly%20in%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20Washington%20will%20now%20have%20difficulty%20in%20devoting%20time%20and%20resources%20to%20its%20primary%20and%20pacing%20threat%E2%80%94China.%20Worse%2C%20the%20chances%20of%20US%20credibility%20taking%20a%20hit%20in%20both%20regional%20wars%20are%20high%20since%20they%20are%20unlikely%20to%20end%20in%20its%20favour.%20President%20Zelenskyy%20of%20Ukraine%20is%20feeling%20the%20heat%20since%20US%20arms%20supplies%20are%20getting%20diverted%20to%20its%20closest%20ally%2C%20Israel.%20Moreover%2C%20Russia%20is%20already%20in%20possession%20of%2023%20per%20cent%20of%20Ukrainian%20territory%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20occupy%20more%20before%20the%20war%20ends%20in%20temporary%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20presents%20the%20US%20with%20a%20big%20dilemma%20since%20it%20cannot%20abandon%20this%20war%20which%20while%20threatening%20to%20enlarge%20into%20a%20wider%20Middle%20East%20confrontation%2C%20has%20no%20solution%20in%20sight.%20Israel%20is%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20the%20two-state%20solution%20and%20the%20Muslim%20world%20will%20reject%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20push%20some%202.3%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20into%20the%20Sinai%20in%20Egypt.%20With%20each%20day%2C%20the%20credibility%20of%20China%20and%20Russia%20is%20rising%20in%20the%20region%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20US.%20Worse%2C%20US%20allies%20and%20partners%20in%20east%20Asia%20watching%20the%20two%20regional%20wars%20might%20start%20assessing%20the%20US%20as%20an%20unreliable%20security%20partner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThus%2C%20even%20as%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20new%20Cold%20War%20in%20a%20fragmented%20world%20is%20unfolding%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20of%20%E2%80%98cooperation%20in%20an%20interdependent%20world%E2%80%99%20with%20BRI%20as%20its%20roadmap%20is%20gaining%20greater%20acceptability%20amongst%20Global%20South%20nations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConscious%20of%20this%2C%20Xi%2C%20at%20the%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20BRF%20announced%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20BRI%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20called%20%E2%80%98small%2C%20yet%20smart.%E2%80%99%20While%20earmarking%20US%24%20107%20billion%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20Xi%20said%20that%20the%20BRI%E2%80%99s%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20projects%20involving%20science%20and%20technology.%20He%20was%20referring%20to%20taking%20most%20BRI%20nations%20into%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20industrial%20revolutions%20depending%20upon%20their%20level%20of%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20this%20new%20strategy%2C%20Xi%20highlighted%20four%20areas%20of%20partnership.%20First%2C%20Xi%20announced%20a%20new%20initiative%20called%20%E2%80%98Global%20AI%20Governance%20Initiative%E2%80%99%2C%20his%20fourth%20in%2010%20years%20of%20BRI%3B%20the%20other%20three%20being%20the%20Global%20Development%20Initiative%2C%20Global%20Security%20Initiative%2C%20and%20Global%20Civilisation%20Initiative.%20The%20present%20initiative%20involving%20AI%20and%20data%20would%20be%20done%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20BRI%20nations.%20China%20will%20set%20the%20technology%20standards%2C%20while%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20partnership%20with%20host%20nations%20will%20determine%20rules%2C%20regulations%2C%20and%20norms%20for%20use%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20for%20development.%20Thus%2C%20China%20will%20help%20set%20up%20data%20centres%2C%20cloud%20services%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20range%20of%20AI%20activities%20like%20data%20collection%2C%20algorithm%20design%2C%20technology%20development%2C%20technology%20production%2C%20and%20applications.%20To%20facilitate%20the%20applications%2C%20Xi%20proposed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fmfa_eng%2Fzxxx_662805%2F202310%2Ft20231020_11164505.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esetting%20up%20of%20100%2C000%20%E2%80%98training%20opportunities%E2%80%99%20in%20BRI%20nations%20by%202030%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20level%20of%20industrial%20internet%20development%20presupposes%20that%20advancement%20in%20third%20industrial%20revolution%20with%20Chinese%20help%20would%20be%20underway%20or%20completed%20in%20three%20specific%20areas%3A%20fibre%20optic%20cables%2C%20sea%20cables%2C%20and%20Chinese%20Baidu%20global%20satellite%20system.%20Unlike%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20Global%20Position%20System%20with%2031%20satellites%2C%20the%20Baidu%20system%20is%20a%20constellation%20of%2045%20satellites%20with%20ability%20for%20two-way%20beaming%2C%20which%20means%20that%20in%20the%20remotest%20areas%20where%20satellite%20ground%20stations%20are%20not%20available%2C%20communication%20can%20be%20done%20directly%20between%20sender%20and%20receiver%20through%20satellite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecond%2C%20to%20mitigate%20climate%20change%20disasters%2C%20China%20has%20proposed%20green%20development%20for%20BRI%20nations.%20This%20is%20doable%20since%20China%20is%20a%20world%20leader%20in%20solar%20panels%2C%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20and%20Lithium-ion%20batteries.%20The%20latter%20will%20soon%20be%20supplemented%20by%20Sodium-ion%20batteries%2C%20which%20while%20cheaper%20than%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20will%20give%20similar%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThird%2C%20connectivity%20with%20focus%20on%20rail%20links%20with%20the%20China-Europe%20Railway%20Express%20as%20the%20flagship%20project.%20Once%20again%2C%20China%20is%20a%20global%20leader%20in%20rail%20connectivity%20and%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20high%20speed%20%E2%80%93%20350km%2Fhour%20%E2%80%93%20network.%20Moreover%2C%20in%20June%202021%2C%20China%20successfully%20showcased%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20MagLev%20(Magnetic%20Levitation)%20train%20with%20600km%2Fhour%20speed.%20By%202025%2C%20China%20will%20have%20five%20more%20Maglev%20trains%20which%20it%20has%20proposed%20to%20be%20an%20intermediate%20mode%20of%20travel%20between%20railways%20and%20commercial%20aeroplanes.%20The%20moot%20point%20is%20that%20by%20setting%20standards%20in%20AI%2C%20fast%20rails%2C%20and%20green%20development%20in%20BRI%20nations%2C%20China%20will%20have%20an%20unbeatable%20lead%20in%20international%20standards%20setting%20which%20will%20provide%20first%20user%20advantage%20to%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20Global%20South%20nations%2C%20and%20later%2C%20most%20of%20the%20world.%20And%20fourth%2C%20Xi%20expressed%20the%20need%20for%20establishing%20a%20BRI%20secretariat%2C%20which%2C%20given%20the%20increasing%20footprint%20of%20BRI%20plus%20Greater%20Eurasia%20nations%2C%20would%20be%20necessary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20making%20Greater%20Eurasia%20a%20reality%2C%20Putin%20spoke%20at%20the%20BRF%20about%20the%20urgency%20to%20develop%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20far%20east%20by%20opening%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route%20which%20provides%20the%20shortest%20shipping%20lane%20from%20Europe%20to%20East%20Asia%20through%20the%20Bering%20Strait.%20According%20to%20Putin%2C%20starting%202024%2C%20ice-class%20cargo%20ships%20will%20be%20able%20to%20operate%20on%20this%20route%20round%20the%20year.%20Moreover%2C%20with%20Russia%20assuming%20the%20BRICS%20presidency%20in%202024%2C%20development%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20far%20east%20from%20Vladivostok%20to%20East%20Cape%20will%20be%20a%20priority.%20This%20includes%20the%20Siberian%20and%20Sakhalin%20gas%20pipelines.%20After%20all%2C%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20Arctic%20which%20accounts%20for%2030%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20territory%20across%20three%20time%20zones%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Farticles%2Fenergy-fact-sheet-why-does-russian-oil-and-gas-matter%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%2020%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20oil%20and%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20gas%20reserves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Russian%20Arctic%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Northern%20Sea%20route%20are%20being%20developed%20with%20Chinese%20help.%20Given%20this%2C%20joint%20naval%20patrols%20by%20Russian%20and%20Chinese%20navies%20in%20the%20Arctic%20region%20for%20peace%20and%20stability%20has%20raised%20US%20heckles%20as%20the%20Bering%20Strait%20runs%20close%20to%20Alaska.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20this%20area%20has%20become%20a%20region%20of%20great%20power%20contestation%2C%20it%20has%20become%20another%20impetus%20for%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20%E2%80%98no%20limits%E2%80%99%20partnership.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20belief%20that%20dislike%20of%20the%20US%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20Chinese%20and%20Russian%20partnership%2C%20it%20is%20the%20integration%20of%20their%20global%20visions%20which%20will%20see%20them%20working%20together%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWestern%20analysts%20wonder%20whether%20China%20and%20Russia%20will%20form%20an%20alliance%20like%20NATO%20where%20an%20attack%20on%20one%20will%20be%20considered%20an%20attack%20on%20all.%20This%20will%20not%20happen.%20Global%20powers%20like%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20alliances%20among%20themselves.%20They%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20defend%20their%20own%20territorial%20integrity.%20Smaller%20powers%20seek%20alliances%20with%20major%20powers%20for%20collective%20security.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20an%20alliance%20or%20military%20bloc%20runs%20against%20the%20spirit%20of%20global%20cooperation%20that%20China%20and%20Russia%20are%20collectively%20seeking.%20And%20that%20is%20how%20they%20are%20offering%20an%20alternate%20vision%20to%20the%20Global%20South%E2%80%94security%20through%20cooperation%20and%20interdependence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EPravin%20Sawhney%E2%80%99s%20recent%20book%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16090026%2FUntitled-design-6-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fas-biden-and-xi-meet-whats-at-stake-is-two-competing-visions-for-the-world%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Global%20South%2C%20barring%20India%2C%20is%20increasingly%20attracted%20by%20China%E2%80%99s%20cooperation-driven%20approach%20to%20global%20development%20and%20put%20off%20by%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20emphasis%20on%20competition%20and%20confrontation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fas-biden-and-xi-meet-whats-at-stake-is-two-competing-visions-for-the-world%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Headlines%20may%20be%20about%20Virat%20%26amp%3B%20Shami%2C%20but%20actual%20hero%20is%20...%20'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105385000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105248773%2Cimgsize-84646.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Fworld-cup-headlines-may-be-about-virat-kohli-mohammed-shami-but-the-actual-hero-is-%2Farticleshow%2F105248466.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20were%20many%20in%20the%20list%20of%20Indian%20performers%20who%20can%20be%20credited%20for%20the%2070-run%20triumph.%20Virat%20Kohli's%20record-breaking%2050th%20ODI%20century%2C%20Shreyas%20Iyer's%20second%20consecutive%20hundred%2C%20the%20start%20provided%20by%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20and%20the%20seven-wicket%20spell%20by%20the%20unplayable%20Mohammed%20Shami%20all%20proved%20decisive%20in%20India's%20entry%20into%20the%20final.%20But%20among%20all%20those%20names%2C%20one%20that%20stands%20out%20for%20former%20England%20skipper%20Nasser%20Hussain%20is%20the%20skipper.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Subrata%20Roy%20Foretold%20New%20India%E2%80%99s%20New%20Crony%20Capitalism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16085101%2FUntitled-design-5-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20death%20of%20Subrata%20Roy%20of%20the%20Sahara%20Group%20provides%20a%20much-needed%20occasion%20to%20meditate%20on%20the%20inseparability%20of%20the%20business%20community%20and%20the%20political%20class%20in%20modern%20India.%20Saharashri%2C%20as%20Roy%20called%20himself%2C%20came%20to%20personify%20a%20key%20facet%20of%20our%20political%20economy%3A%20that%20money%20power%20can%20thrive%20and%20prosper%20only%20if%20friendly%20%E2%80%98political%20power%E2%80%99%20is%20available.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecall%20the%20closing%20days%20of%20Shining%20India.%20It%20is%20February%202004.%20The%20saffron%20crowd%20had%20convinced%20itself%20that%20it%20was%20coming%20back%20to%20power%20for%20another%20five%20years%20in%20a%20few%20months.%20And%20Saharashri%20had%20decided%20to%20use%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20weddings%20of%20both%20his%20sons%20to%20showcase%20his%20connectivity%20with%20political%20players%20of%20all%20hues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F04%2F04192003%2Fstatecraft.png%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-237577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22233%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20A.B.%20Vajpayee%20travelled%20in%20an%20Air%20Force%20plane%20to%20Lucknow%20for%20the%20Sahara%20wedding%3B%20deputy%20prime%20minister%2C%20L.K.%20Advani%20was%20not%20one%20to%20sit%20out%3B%20many%20central%20ministers%20like%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh%20felt%20obliged%20to%20honour%20the%20invite%3B%20even%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20India%2C%20Bhairon%20Singh%20Shekhawat%2C%20unmindful%20of%20the%20protocol%20and%20dignity%20of%20his%20high%20office%2C%20allowed%20himself%20to%20be%20persuaded%20to%20attend%3B%20chief%20ministers%20like%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20and%20Laloo%20Prasad%20came%3B%20and%2C%20so%20did%20Congress%20leaders%20like%20Digvijay%20Singh%2C%20Ahmed%20Patel%20and%20Murli%20Deora.%20Only%20two%20leaders%20of%20some%20consequence%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh%20chose%20not%20to%20put%20in%20an%20appearance%20(despite%20many%20entreaties%20and%20pleadings).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%20a%20few%20months%20earlier%2C%20Vajpayee%20had%20warned%20against%20the%20possibility%20of%20%E2%80%98loktantra%E2%80%99%20degenerating%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98dhantantra.%E2%80%99%20But%20the%20Saharashri%20had%20managed%20to%20stage%20an%20intimate%20moment%20in%20the%20uncertain%20relationship%20between%20the%20business%2Findustrial%20class%20and%20the%20political%20crowd%3B%20neither%20side%20felt%20apologetic%20about%20the%20company%20it%20was%20keeping.%20But%20that%20evening%20was%20to%20become%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20money%20power%20often%20became%20dependent%20upon%20the%20vicissitudes%20of%20a%20changing%20political%20landscape.%20From%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20his%20fame%20and%20respectability%20in%20February%202004%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98entrepreneur%E2%80%99%20who%20died%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20hospital%20ended%20up%20a%20forgotten%20figure%20because%20the%20political%20economy%20chessboard%20got%20reset%20and%20new%20political%20winners%20came%20in%20with%20their%20own%20business%20friends%20and%20financiers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdmittedly%2C%20the%20business%20community%20has%20a%20legitimate%20stake%20in%20how%20society%20gets%20organised%20and%20how%20it%20is%20governed.%20The%20Indian%20business%20community%2C%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20has%20sought%20a%20voice%20for%20itself%20in%20shaping%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20collective%20future.%20As%20early%20as%20January%201945%2C%20even%20before%20India%20became%20independent%2C%20eight%20business%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20J.R.D.%20Tata%2C%20G.D.%20Birla%2C%20Sir%20Ardeshir%20Rustomjee%20Dalal%2C%20Sir%20Purshottamdas%20Thakurdas%2C%20Ardeshir%20Darabshaw%2C%20Lala%20Shri%20Ram%2C%20Kasturbhai%20Lalbhai%20and%20Dr.%20John%20Mathai%20%E2%80%93%20had%20proposed%20what%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20Bombay%20Plan%2C%20a%20blueprint%20for%20economic%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fcrony-capitalism-on-modis-watch-means-invisible-hands-ensure-you-never-go-bankrupt%5C%22%3ECrony%20Capitalism%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20Means%20Invisible%20Hands%20Ensure%20You%20Never%20Go%20Bankrupt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20post-Independence%20leadership%2C%20awash%20as%20it%20was%20in%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20a%20mass%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20did%20not%20much%20care%20for%20the%20Bombay%20Planners%E2%80%99%20advice%20(%20though%20John%20Mathai%20did%20get%20inducted%20very%20early%20in%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20as%20finance%20minister).%20The%20Bombay%20Plan%20crowd%20liked%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20economic%20intervention%20created%20infrastructure%20they%20were%20not%20capable%20of%20generating%20but%20they%20were%20not%20overly%20amused%20by%20Nehru%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20build%20an%20egalitarian%20social%20order%2C%20with%20%E2%80%98socialistic%E2%80%99%20content.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20business%20groups%20were%20savvy%20enough%20to%20rejig%20their%20resources%20and%20prejudices%20to%20the%20politicians%E2%80%99%20need%20for%20funds.%20The%20business%20community%20was%20pragmatic%20enough%20to%20recognise%2C%20if%20not%20respect%2C%20the%20sanctity%20of%20democratic%20mandates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%201971%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20(post-bank%20nationalisation%20and%20the%20abolition%20of%20privy%20purses)%20was%20perhaps%20the%20only%20time%20when%20the%20business%20leaders%20felt%20agitated%20enough%20to%20openly%20cross%20swords%20with%20sections%20of%20the%20political%20class.%20Industrialists%20like%20K.K.%20Birla%20and%20Naval%20Tata%20entered%20the%20electoral%20arena%20against%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Congress.%20Once%20again%2C%20they%20adjusted%20to%20political%20realities%3B%20and%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20regime%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20did%20not%20try%20to%20carry%20out%20any%20kind%20of%20vendetta%20against%20recalcitrant%20industrialists.%20Soon%20the%20various%20chambers%20of%20commerce%20were%20ordering%20the%20second%20and%20revised%20edition%20of%20the%20book%20of%20protocol%20of%20crony%20capitalism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20following%20two%20decades%20%E2%80%93%20before%20Narasimha%20Rao%20and%20Manmohan%20Singh%20unleashed%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98animal%20spirits%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20the%20political%20leaders%E2%80%99%20need%20and%20appetite%20for%20funds%20(for%20party%20and%20personal%20coffers)%20acquired%20a%20definite%20momentum%20and%20a%20certain%20grudging%20acceptability.%20The%20Dhirubhai%20Syndrome%20was%20to%20get%20consecrated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201991%2C%20Corporate%20India%20came%20of%20age.%20The%20politicians%20not%20only%20vacated%20the%20economy%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98commanding%20heights%E2%80%99%20but%20they%20also%20stepped%20down%20from%20their%20high%20moral%20perch.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edesi%20seths%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20now%20joined%20by%20unscrupulous%20global%20%E2%80%98investors%E2%80%99%20in%20creating%20new%20political%20players%20with%20needs%20and%20greed.%20Governmental%20%E2%80%98stability%E2%80%99%20had%20to%20be%20orchestrated.%20Businessmen%20were%20needed%20with%20whom%20the%20politicians%E2%80%99%20ill-gotten%20funds%20could%20be%20parked.%20And%2C%20a%20political%20leader%E2%80%99s%20association%20with%20shady%20businessman%20was%20not%20looked%20down%20upon%20because%20governmental%20%E2%80%98stability%E2%80%99%20had%20to%20be%20purchased.%20The%20whole%20business%20of%20electoral%20democracy%20became%20exponentially%20expensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20new%20nexus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqz.com%2Findia%2F248685%2Fraghuram-rajan-explains-why-corrupt-politicians-win-elections-in-india%5C%22%3Ewas%20dissected%20insightfully%20by%20Raghuram%20Rajan%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CSo%20the%20circle%20is%20complete.%20The%20crooked%20politician%20needs%20the%20businessman%20to%20provide%20the%20funds%20that%20allow%20him%20to%20supply%20patronage%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20fight%20elections.%20The%20corrupt%20businessman%20needs%20the%20crooked%20politician%20to%20get%20public%20resources%20and%20contracts%20cheaply.%20And%20the%20politician%20needs%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20under-privileged.%20Every%20constituency%20is%20to%20the%20other%20in%20a%20cycle%20of%20dependency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESaharashri%20would%20have%20recognised%20the%20%E2%80%98cycle%20of%20dependency%E2%80%99%20that%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20was%20talking%20about.%20Just%20as%20he%20would%20recognise%20that%20even%20in%20%E2%80%98New%20India%E2%80%99%20that%20cycle%20remains%20not%20only%20unbroken%20but%20has%20been%20refined%20and%20almost%20institutionalised.%20Crony%20capitalism%20now%20goes%20by%20a%20new%20name%20called%20%E2%80%98Vikas.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EHarish%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fhkhare%5C%22%3EKhare%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20former%20editor-in-chief%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Tribune%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700105080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F16085101%2FUntitled-design-5-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsubrata-roy-foretold-new-indias-new-crony-capitalism%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20crooked%20politician%20needs%20the%20businessman%20to%20provide%20the%20funds%20that%20allow%20him%20to%20supply%20patronage%20to%20the%20poor%20and%20fight%20elections.%20The%20corrupt%20businessman%20needs%20the%20crooked%20politician%20to%20get%20public%20resources%20and%20contracts%20cheaply.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fsubrata-roy-foretold-new-indias-new-crony-capitalism%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Virat%20seems%20to%20be%20getting%20better%20...%20'%3A%20Williamson%20warns%20India's%20opponents%22%2C%22content