er.com%2Ftrumps-ny-fraud-trial-opens-today-heres-why-still-matters-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20former%20president's%20Manhattan%20fraud%20trial%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20used%20these%20very%20words%20to%20describe%20the%20creative%20math%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20certainly%20a%20red%20flag%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20testified%20the%20expert%2C%20Jason%20Flemmons%2C%20referring%20to%20an%20internal%2C%20Trump%20Organization%20spreadsheet%20from%202016%20displayed%20on%20overhead%20screens%20in%20the%20lower%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20want%20to%20know%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20said%20of%20the%20spreadsheet%2C%20in%20which%20Trump%20claimed%20some%20%24200%20million%20in%20ready%20cash.%20State%20officials%20say%20those%20millions%20were%20actually%20locked%20in%20a%20partnership%20that%20Trump%20did%20not%20have%20sole%20authority%20to%20withdraw%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20red%20flag%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20in%20the%20non-jury%20trial%2C%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arthur%20Engoron%2C%20cut%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20my%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20Flemmons%20answered%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20rather%20glaring%20issue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20not-so-ready%20cash%20was%20just%20one%20of%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20net-worth%20red%20flags%20identified%20Wednesday%20by%20Flemmons.%20A%20former%20fraud%20enforcer%20for%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%2C%20Flemmons%20had%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-fraud-trial-experts-offer-chillaxed-theory-of-asset-valuation-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestifying%20on%20Trump's%20behalf%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20when%20he%20described%20the%20broad%20wiggle%20room%20allowed%20in%20estimating%20net%