ating%20the%20Buffalo%20River%2C%20a%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENY%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20is%20suing%20PepsiCo%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20company%20is%20polluting%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20seeks%20to%20force%20Pepsi%20and%20Frito-Lay%20to%20clean%20up%20wrappers%20and%20bottles%20on%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Buffalo%20River.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fyou-are-consuming-microplastics-how-much-what-to-know-risks-2022-4%5C%22%3EMicroplastics%20have%20been%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20fish%20species%20and%20in%20Buffalo's%20drinking%20water%20supply%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-letitia-james-fight-over-one-sentence-fraud-trial-testimony-2023-10%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20PepsiCo%20Inc.%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20accusing%20the%20soda-and-snack%20food%20giant%20of%20polluting%20the%20environment%20and%20endangering%20public%20health%20after%20its%20single-use%20plastics%20were%20found%20along%20the%20Buffalo%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcourt-filings%2Fpepsico-complaint.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20in%20state%20Supreme%20Court%20aims%20to%20require%20PepsiCo%20and%20its%20subsidiaries%2C%20Frito-Lay%20Inc.%20and%20Frito-Lay%20North%20America%20Inc.%2C%20to%20clean%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-of-the-global-population-wants-single-use-plastics-banned-2022-2%5C%22%3Esingle-use%20plastic%20packaging%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20food%20wrappers%20and%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20that%20have%20found%20a%20way%20to%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Buffalo%20River%20and%20watershed%2C%20contaminating%20drinking%20water%20supply%20for%20the%20city%20of%20Buffalo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20company%20is%20too%20big%20to%20ensure%20that%20their%20products%20do%20not%20damage%20our%20environment%20and%20public%20health.%20All%20New%20Yorkers%20have%20a%20basic%20right%20to%20clean%20water%2C%20yet%20PepsiCo's%20irresponsible%20packaging%20and%20marketing%20endanger%20Buffalo's%20water%20supply%2C%20environment%2C%20and%20public%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fag.ny.gov%2Fpress-release%2F2023%2Fattorney-general-james-takes-historic-action-against-pepsico-endangering%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsi-says-people-skipping-meals-great-for-business-2023-10%5C%22%3EPepsiCo%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20single%20largest%20identifiable%20contributor%20to%20the%20plastic%20waste%20contaminating%20the%20Buffalo%20River%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20Of%20the%201%2C916%20pieces%20of%20plastic%20waste%20containing%20an%20identifiable%20brand%2C%2017.1%25%20were%20produced%20by%20PepsiCo%2C%20according%20to%20a%202022%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20state%20Office%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmail%20messages%20left%20for%20a%20spokesperson%20at%20PepsiCo%20were%20not%20immediately%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicroplastics%20have%20also%20been%20found%20in%20fish%20species%20that%20are%20known%20to%20inhabit%20Lake%20Erie%20and%20the%20Buffalo%20River%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Buffalo's%20drinking%20water%20supply%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20Exposure%20to%20those%20chemicals%20can%20carry%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmicroplastics-carry-stomach-viruses-in-fresh-water-for-days-study-2022-6%5C%22%3Eadverse%20health%20effects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Buffalo%20River%20was%20once%20considered%20one%20of%20the%20most%20polluted%20rivers%20in%20the%20United%20States%20until%20the%20state's%20Department%20of%20Environmental%20Conservation%20stepped%20in%20with%20a%20remedial%20action%20plan%20in%201989%20to%20restore%20the%20river's%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Buffalo%20community%20fought%20for%20over%2050%20years%20to%20secure%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20to%20clean%20up%20toxic%20pollution%2C%20improve%20habitat%2C%20and%20restore%20communities%20around%20the%20Buffalo%20River%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jill%20Jedlicka%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20Buffalo%20Niagara%20Waterkeeper%2C%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20not%20sit%20idly%20by%20as%20our%20waterways%20become%20polluted%20again%2C%20this%20time%20from%20ever-growing%20single-use%20plastic%20pollution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20James%20is%20also%20calling%20for%20PepsiCo%20to%20stop%20selling%20or%20distributing%20any%20product%20in%20the%20Buffalo%20region%20without%20warning%20consumers%20about%20the%20potential%20health%20and%20environmental%20risks%20of%20its%20packaging.%20It%20also%20asks%20that%20the%20company%20take%20steps%20to%20prevent%20additional%20plastic%20pollution%20from%C2%A0entering%20the%20Buffalo%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPepsiCo%2C%20which%20is%20headquartered%20in%20New%20York%2C%20produces%20and%20packages%20at%20least%2085%20different%20beverage%20brands%20including%20Gatorade%20and%20Pepsi%20products%2C%20and%20at%20least%2025%20snack%20food%20brands%20that%20mostly%20come%20in%20single-use%20plastic%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20past%20years%2C%20the%20company%20has%20repeatedly%20pledged%20that%20it%20would%20make%20meaningful%20strides%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsi-climate-change-supply-chain-clean-energy-regenerative-agriculture-plastic-pollution%5C%22%3Ereduce%20its%20use%20of%20plastics%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20lawsuit%20alleges%20that%20the%20opposite%20is%20happening%2C%20and%20that%20PepsiCo%20misled%20the%20public%20about%20its%20efforts%20to%20combat%20plastic%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-sues-pepsi-frito-lay-force-clean-plastic-pollution-buffalo-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700081875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65552fa44ca513d8242a29d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-sues-pepsi-frito-lay-force-clean-plastic-pollution-buffalo-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Food%20wrappers%20and%20plastic%20bottles%20at%20the%20shores%20of%20the%20Buffalo%20River%20and%20watershed%20are%20contaminating%20the%20city's%20drinking%20water%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Insider%20Inc.)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fny-sues-pepsi-frito-lay-force-clean-plastic-pollution-buffalo-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Qatar%20seeking%20deal%20to%20free%2050%20hostages%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700081165000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105243658%2Cimgsize-1390942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fqatar-seeking-deal-to-free-50-hostages-report%2Farticleshow%2F105243636.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105243636.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EQatari%20mediators%20were%20on%20Wednesday%20seeking%20to%20negotiate%20a%20deal%20between%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%20that%20includes%20the%20release%20of%20around%2050%20civilian%20hostages%20from%20Gaza%20in%20exchange%20for%2