9COther%20women%20in%20the%20village%2C%20who%20were%20providing%20training%20in%20making%20bamboo%20products%2C%20informed%20me%20that%20they%20would%20also%20offer%20employment%20once%20we%20completed%20our%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20her%20enthusiasm%20was%20curbed%20by%20the%20people%20around%20her.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20neighbours%20and%20our%20family%20friends%20were%20against%20sending%20the%20women%20of%20the%20house%20outside%20to%20work.%20They%20doubted%20our%20ability%20to%20earn%20anything%2C%20but%20my%20mother-in-law%20stood%20up%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20then%2C%20both%20Namita%20and%20her%20sister-in-law%20had%20also%20assumed%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F255089%2Fdr-m-aishwarya-coimbatore-parenting-network-tamil-nadu-taboo-how-to-donate-breast-milk-feeding-awareness-taboo-myths-banks-postpartum-depression-covid-19-pandemic-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20role%20of%20mothers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20had%20additional%20responsibilities.%20%E2%80%9COur%20husbands%20and%20my%20mother-in-law%20decided%20to%20show%20faith%20in%20us%20and%20gave%20us%20immense%20support%20to%20go%20for%20the%20training%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother-in-law%20would%20take%20care%20of%20our%20kids%20when%20we%20attended%20the%20training%20sessions.%20She%20would%20also%20help%20us%20in%20household%20work%20and%20ensure%20we%20had%20enough%20time%20to%20perfect%20our%20craft%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20was%20being%20held%20by%20an%20NGO%20called%20%E2%80%98Keshav%20Srushti%E2%80%99%20headed%20by%20Gaurav%20Shrivastava.%20It%20was%20an%20initiative%20to%20promote%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%20and%20make%20them%20financially%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20initiative%2C%20Gaurav%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20initiative%2