from%20Khakes%20village%20in%20Kalahandi%2C%20was%20forced%20to%20return%20home%20by%20the%20police%20from%20the%20borders%20for%20not%20carrying%20his%20Aadhar%20card.%20He%20casked%20the%20police%20personnel%20with%20anger%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20flows%20from%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20our%20area%2C%20does%20it%20seek%20permission%20from%20the%20officers%20before%20entering%20Rayagada%20or%20Kalahandi%3F%20The%20water%20that%20originates%20from%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0reaches%20Kalahandi%20and%20flows%20ahead%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENagabali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20whose%20permission%20has%20it%20taken%20%3F%E2%80%9D%20Like%20Malaya%2C%20several%20others%20were%20stopped%20from%20crossing%20the%20borders%20or%20forced%20to%20return%20home%20at%20various%20check%20points%20for%20not%20carrying%20Aadhar%20cards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20heavy%20repression%20and%20the%20threat%20of%20arrests%2C%20hundreds%20of%20people%20from%20villages%20across%20Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gathered%20at%20the%20public%20hearing%20venue%20at%20Sunger%20chanting%20slogans%20like%20%E2%80%98Vedanta-Mythri%20Company%2C%20go%20back%E2%80%99.%20Placards%20reading%20%E2%80%98Tijmali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20ours%2C%20not%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20private%20property%20to%20be%20mined%E2%80%99%20filled%20the%20venue.%20Amidst%20heavy%20deployment%20of%20police%20and%20eight%20platoons%20of%20paramilitary%20personnel%2C%20nearly%202%2C000%20people%20unitedly%20registered%20their%20dissent%20at%20the%20public%20hearing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15163409%2Funnamed-7.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20wi