.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20October%2027%2C%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20army%20has%20lost%20nine%20towns%20where%20its%20battalions%20had%20been%20based%20for%20decades%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irrawaddy.com%2Fnews%2Fwar-against-the-junta%2Fnine-towns-occupied-by-myanmar-military-for-decades-lost-to-resistance-in-days.html%5C%22%3EMyanmar%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Irrawady%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaw%20Min%20Tun%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20military%20leadership%2C%20said%20that%20the%20rebel%20groups%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdestroying%20the%20whole%20country%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20claims%20of%20captured%20military%20posts%20were%20%E2%80%9Cpropaganda%E2%80%9D%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20enemies%20retreated%20after%20they%20lost%20soldiers.%20We%20are%20trying%20to%20combine%20small%20posts%20strategically%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20reported%20him%20as%20also%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Myanmar%20military%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fmyanmar-military-unable-to-counter-resistance-offensive%5C%22%3Eadmitted%20to%20losing%20control%20of%20some%20towns%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Shan%20state%2C%20and%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20President%20Myint%20Swe%20said%20last%20week%20that%20the%20country%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmyanmar-at-risk-of-breaking-apart-junta-backed-leader-says%2Fa-67351290%5C%22%3Emay%20face%20an%20existential%20threat%20from%20the%20rebel%20action%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20does%20not%20effectively%20manage%20the%20incidents%20happening%20in%20the%20border%20region%2C%20the%20country%20will%20be%20split%20into%20various%20parts%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20clashes%20in%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20northeast%2C%20the%20AA%20has%20also%20launched%20attacks%20against%20the%20m