g%20white%20mud%20(%3Cem%3Echuhi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20red%20mud%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20black%20mud%20(charcoal%20black).%20Festivals%20and%20weddings%20in%20the%20village%20were%20my%20favourite%20occasions%20since%20there%20would%20be%20opportunities%20for%20me%20to%20make%20%3Cem%3Edignas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20form%20of%20tribal%20art%20practised%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Gond%20community)%20on%20the%20home%20walls%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%2050%2C%20one%20would%20say%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333114%2Fkolkata-artist-kishore-pratim-biswas-paints-steam-locomotives%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eart%20is%20in%20her%20genes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20she%20replicates%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20style.%20This%20time%20on%20canvas%20and%20walls%20that%20are%20hundreds%20of%20feet%20tall.%20Vyam%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20prowess%20led%20her%20to%20win%20many%20accolades%20throughout%20her%20career%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20being%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20her%20niche%20in%20the%20art%20world%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transition%20from%20mud%20walls%20to%20canvas%20happened%20in%201996%20when%20Durgabai%20married%20Subhash%20Vyam%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Bhopal%20and%20a%20sculptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20679px)%20100vw%2C%20679px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-194924_11zon-1699971669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22679%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Durgabai's%20paintings%20are%20centred%20around%20nature%20and%20Gond%20myths%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FScreenshot-2023-11-14-194924_11zon-1699971669.jpg%20679w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterind