-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334031%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAsha%20(second%20from%20the%20right%20in%20the%20last%20row)%20with%20her%20family%20and%20neighbours%20in%20Japan.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20easy%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%20then.%20They%20used%20to%20write%20messages%20on%20very%20thin%20rice%20papers%2C%20stitch%20them%20into%20blankets%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20shipmen%2C%20it%20would%20be%20sent%20to%20Netaji%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tanvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20parents%20remained%20dedicated%20to%20the%20freedom%20movement%2C%20Asha%20continued%20her%20schooling%20in%20Showa%20University%20at%20Tokyo.%20She%20discontinued%20her%20education%20after%20joining%20the%20Rani%20Jhansi%20regiment%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017.%20From%20Tokyo%2C%20she%20went%20to%20the%20training%20camp%20in%20Bangkok%20without%20any%20proper%20channels%20of%20transport%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20language%20being%20a%20barrier%20as%20Asha%20grew%20up%20speaking%20Japanese%2C%20she%20made%20friends%20at%20the%20regiment.%20The%20story%20becomes%20humorous%20and%20thrilling%20when%20she%20writes%20about%20learning%20Hindi%20and%20firing%20a%20machine%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20book%2C%20she%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20honest%2C%20anything%2C%20including%20a%20bomb%20falling%20on%20my%20head%20will%20be%20easier%20than%20learning%20how%20to%20write%20Hindi.%E2%80%9D%20In%20fact%20when%20she%20was%20offered%20%3Cem%3Emakki%20ki%20roti%20%3C%2Fem%3Eby%20an%20Indian%20family%2C%20she%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3Echapati%20%3C%2Fem%3E(flatbread)%20made%20of%20flies!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Bangkok%2C%20she%20was%20trained%20to%20use%20machine%20guns%2C%20how%20to%20hold%20and