0equipped%20with%20a%20petrol%20engine%20as%20a%20standby%20power%20source%20to%20ensure%20complete%20reliability%20for%20the%20consumer%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20came%20to%20Ashish.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20built%20the%20hybrid%20as%20a%20retrofit%20solution%20to%20give%20a%20bridge%20to%2025%20crore%20existing%20two-wheeler%20riders%20in%20the%20country%20towards%20a%20greener%20tomorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20early%202020%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%2015%20years%20of%20corporate%20career%20and%20finally%20bring%20his%20childhood%20dream%20to%20a%20living%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20the%20company%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332299%2Fbengaluru-chef-elizabeth-yorke-upcycles-brewery-byproducts-into-sustainable-food-items%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresent%20in%20Bengaluru%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20has%20converted%20over%2050%20vehicles%20into%20their%20hybrid%20models.%20Of%20those%2025%20were%20brought%20to%20the%20company%20by%20the%20consumers%20themselves.%20It%20has%20received%20ARAI%20%26amp%3B%20RTO%20approval%20to%20convert%20all%20major%20brands%20of%20scooters%20up%20to%20125cc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20converted%20vehicles%20have%20undergone%20rigorous%20testing%2C%20covering%20a%20total%20distance%20of%20one%20and%20a%20half%20to%20two%20lakh%20kilometres%20over%20the%20past%2018%20months.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHigher%20range%2C%20cheaper%20transition%20and%20additional%20features%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-2-1699540345.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%